reviewText: Great videos and classic interview footage, plus a look inside Hank's mail-order headquarters! A real bargain if you get it for $10 or less. All the videos except 'If It Will, It Will' are on DVD releases.
For the Hank Jr fan in all of us.

I kinda wanted more music videos on it,yet with the interview and the classic hit music videos from the music legend son of Hank Williams Sr. who was a music legend in his own right,buy this video tpe. You really can't go wrong with it,unless you hate rowdy stuff,other than that,you should buy it. It is perfect for Hank Williams Jr. Fan parties. Trust me on that.
